00:00:22,490 --> 00:00:26,225
narrator: today on "how it's made"...  

5
00:00:26,227 --> 00:00:28,160
...leather overnight bags...  

6
00:00:32,233 --> 00:00:33,900
...horse exercisers...     

7
00:00:37,972 --> 00:00:39,805
...air hockey tables...    

8
00:00:44,111 --> 00:00:46,078
...and copper sculptures.   

9
